{"tid":1569952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"915 銅鑼灣如果狗狗大圍捕 大家有咩對策","createTime":"2019-09-14T21:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:50:47.000Z","uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59778ed2a67fd506d2984f20e696c8bcdaa57db8","tid":1569952,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:26:02.000Z","msg":"每次入夜一定大圍捕 而家地鐵直頭封埋<br />\n巴士都有機會被人搜 所以我認為入夜前就做好所有抗爭活動<br />\nhit and run 如果真係有需要留夜既 諗定真正安全路線<br />\n如果唔得既就盡量係附近安全地方留到天光先走<br />\n以上只係建議 一切由現場人士決定<br />\n<br />\nbtw 今日洶大打藍屍打得好 好開心大家又進化左<br />\n但仲未夠 下次見到打幾分鐘就好走 因為佢地一定叫狗狗黎保護佢地<br />\n打幾分鐘之後 係狗黎前大家一齊走 <br />\n狗黎到得個吉提唔到人一肚氣 藍屍又無仇報 諗起都正"},{"pid":"bb542984fe6f60ba4e0f661d9e0dc0d3815cd4a4","tid":1569952,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:29:07.000Z","msg":"唔好再講「散水」  試下改口叫「轉場」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d0b5f8ed3c49e40cc020b8bb4d1cff64126b72","tid":1569952,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:54:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span> <br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"7de31201ce87e4556f77e08e6d3b8364c47f308b","tid":1569952,"uid":216985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb542984fe6f60ba4e0f661d9e0dc0d3815cd4a4","tid":1569952,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T21:29:07.000Z","msg":"唔好再講「散水」  試下改口叫「轉場」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T23:57:28.000Z","msg":"點轉？"},{"pid":"26dda5c2988a362446703d5dd8231c2c2e0f7097","tid":1569952,"uid":54243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb542984fe6f60ba4e0f661d9e0dc0d3815cd4a4","tid":1569952,"uid